  "body_html": "<p class=\"isSelectedEnd\"> </p>\n<p class=\"isSelectedEnd\"><span>The clean girl fragrance in a bottle.</span></p>\n<p class=\"isSelectedEnd\"><span>Creamy fig, soft florals, and silky sandalwood melt into warm skin, creating a scent that feels fresh, expensive, and effortlessly put together. Think glowing skin, white linen, gold jewelry, and a summer spent somewhere beautiful.</span></p>\n<p class=\"isSelectedEnd\"><span>Notes:</span><br><span>Fig • Cassis • Water Lily • Iris • Jasmine • Sandalwood • Vanilla • Patchouli • Soft Musk</span></p>\n<p><span>Wear it when:</span><br><span>You want to smell naturally good. Perfect for everyday wear, sunny afternoons, date nights, vacations, and those moments when you want people to ask, \"What are you wearing?”</span></p>",
